00:37:53.600 --> 00:37:55.640
You would ideally, actually,
ask some more questions as well.

00:37:55.640 --> 00:37:57.290
I mean, the focus on
Mappiness, really,

00:37:57.290 --> 00:37:58.780
was let's look at
natural environment,

00:37:58.780 --> 00:38:00.270
and let's make it
so quick and easy

00:38:00.270 --> 00:38:03.510
that possibly some people
will want to do it.

00:38:03.510 --> 00:38:05.240
So in retrospect,
