00:46:48.490 --> 00:46:49.250
and make that join up.

00:46:49.250 --> 00:46:50.875
So I couldn't have
ever said to people,

00:46:50.875 --> 00:46:52.909
you'll definitely be
part of the research.

00:46:52.909 --> 00:46:54.450
But yeah, definitely
it will be good.

00:46:54.450 --> 00:46:55.908
And that would
also, I guess, speak

00:46:55.908 --> 00:46:58.530
potentially to this question of
different cultures and so on.

00:46:58.530 --> 00:47:01.284
And that would be
interesting to do.

