SPEAKER ONE: We have time
for one more question.

00:53:03.010 --> 00:53:04.710
Any last question?

00:53:04.710 --> 00:53:05.490
If not--

00:53:05.490 --> 00:53:06.080
GEORGE MACKERRON: I
mean, to be honest,

00:53:06.080 --> 00:53:08.400
the thing that surprised me most
